PN,40201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784112473
OL,3,CLargest naval base in Western Europe
OL,4,Creceives record investment
OL,6,FPlymouth's Devonport dockyard will
OL,7,Freceive #7 billion in investment to
OL,8,Fboost its submarine availability.
OL,10,FThere will be critical upgrades to
OL,11,Fdocking facilities and waterfront
OL,12,Finfrastructure at His Majesty's Naval
OL,13,FBase (HMNB) Devonport, which is based
OL,14,Fin Plymouth, and is the largest naval
OL,15,Fbase in Western Europe.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784112473
OL,3,CLargest naval base in Western Europe
OL,4,Creceives record investment
OL,6,FIt forms part of a #26 billion
OL,7,Finvestment in the Royal Navy's naval
OL,8,Fbases - making it the largest
OL,9,Fprogramme of naval infrastructure
OL,10,Finvestment since the end of the Cold
OL,11,FWar.
OL,13,FDefence Minister Luke Pollard MP, also
OL,14,Fthe local MP for Plymouth Sutton and
OL,15,FDavenport, says the move will
OL,16,Freinforce Devonport's position of
OL,17,Fmaintaining the Navy's submarines.
OL,19,FThe Ministry of Defence say that the
OL,20,Finvestment will support "thousands of
OL,21,Fskilled jobs" in the South West.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784112473
OL,3,CLargest naval base in Western Europe
OL,4,Creceives record investment
OL,6,FThe investment will go towards
OL,7,Fmodernising Davenport's facilities,
OL,8,Fincluding rebuilding docks to fit and
OL,9,Fservice the Navy's newest, high-tech
OL,10,Fsubmarines.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, the site is getting a new
OL,13,F"stable-water" berth so ships can be
OL,14,Fworked on regardless of the tide,
OL,15,Falongside a general upgrade of
OL,16,Fbuildings and power systems.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784112473
OL,3,CLargest naval base in Western Europe
OL,4,Creceives record investment
OL,6,FLuke Pollard MP, Member of Parliament
OL,7,Ffor Plymouth Sutton and Devonport,
OL,8,Fsaid: "After a decade where the future
OL,9,Fof Devonport was in question, this new
OL,10,Finvestment secures the future of our
OL,11,Fnaval base and the dockyard for
OL,12,Fdecades to come. It's a flagship day
OL,13,Ffor Devonport.
OL,15,F"As Devonport's MP, I've been proud to
OL,16,Fmake the case for future work in
OL,17,Fsubmarine maintenance and the exciting
OL,18,Fopportunities that marine autonomy and
OL,19,Fthe hybrid navy offer the navy and our
OL,20,Fcity.
OL,26,@pD@GOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784112473
OL,3,CLargest naval base in Western Europe
OL,4,Creceives record investment
OL,6,F"This funding boost is a huge boost
OL,7,Ffor the thousands of people employed
OL,8,Fin Devonport, and a beacon to attract
OL,9,Fthe workers we need as dockyard
OL,10,Femployment grows.
OL,12,F"When I said that this government
OL,13,Fwould back Devonport, I meant it, and
OL,14,Fthis announcement is proof of it."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUvD@bO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784112473
OL,3,CLargest naval base in Western Europe
OL,4,Creceives record investment
OL,6,FCouncillor Tudor Evans OBE, Leader of
OL,7,FPlymouth City Council, said: "It is
OL,8,Falready incredibly transformational
OL,9,Fthat the Government are spending
OL,10,F#4.4bn in our dockyard but to hear
OL,11,Ftoday that we will see a near doubling
OL,12,Fof defence expenditure in our city is
OL,13,Fbeyond our wildest dreams."
OL,26,@oD@^OUuD@[O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
