OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784112473
OL,3,CLargest naval base in Western Europe
OL,4,Creceives record investment
OL,6,FDefence Minister Lord Coaker said:
OL,7,F"Our Navy deserve the best because
OL,8,Fthey do so much to keep us safe in a
OL,9,Fworld that is more dangerous. That is
OL,10,Fwhy we are investing #26bn now to
OL,11,Fensure our Royal Navy has the bases
OL,12,Fand infrastructure it needs for the
OL,13,Ffuture.
OL,15,F"This record investment is the biggest
OL,16,Fupgrade to our naval bases for decades
OL,17,Fand will help secure jobs and
OL,18,Fstrengthen our Armed Forces for years
OL,19,Fto come."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
